    <entry>
      <title>MEOW使用手册</title>
      <link href="/2024/11/18/MEOW%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C/"/>
      <url>/2024/11/18/MEOW%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="MEOW使用手册"><a href="#MEOW使用手册" class="headerlink" title="MEOW使用手册"></a>MEOW使用手册</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;<span class="string">%</span> <span class="string">linkcard</span> <span class="string">%</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">page</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Meow-Theme-Guide</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://chanwj.github.io/Meow-Theme-Guide</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">icon:</span> <span class="string">https://chanwj.github.io/img/site-icon.png</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">desc:</span> <span class="string">MEOW主题指南</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">page</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Pug</span> <span class="string">模板引擎中文文档</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://www.pugjs.cn/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">icon:</span> <span class="string">https://www.pugjs.cn/img/logo.png</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">desc:</span> <span class="string">Pug</span> <span class="string">模板引擎中文文档</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;<span class="string">%</span> <span class="string">endlinkcard</span> <span class="string">%</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>主题使用pug进行渲染</strong></p><h3 id="生成目录功能"><a href="#生成目录功能" class="headerlink" title="生成目录功能"></a>生成目录功能</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="string">or</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="about页面-联系方式"><a href="#about页面-联系方式" class="headerlink" title="about页面-联系方式"></a>about页面-联系方式</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">contact_info:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="网站背景"><a href="#网站背景" class="headerlink" title="网站背景"></a>网站背景</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">background:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">color:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;MistyRose&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">image_url:</span> <span class="string">img/Spiritfarer-1.png</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">gradient:</span> <span class="string">linear-gradient(to</span> <span class="string">bottom</span> <span class="string">right,#ffa751,#ffe259)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">配置项</th><th align="center">名称</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">type</td><td align="center">背景类型</td></tr><tr><td align="center">color</td><td align="center">背景颜色</td></tr><tr><td align="center">image_url</td><td align="center">背景图片路径</td></tr><tr><td align="center">gradient</td><td align="center">渐变语句</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="网站字体"><a href="#网站字体" class="headerlink" title="网站字体"></a>网站字体</h3><p><strong>1.导入字体库链接</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">font:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url_list:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400..700&amp;display=swap&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif&amp;display=swap&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300..700&amp;display=swap&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2.配置字体名称，顺序从前至后</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">font_family:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&#x27;Noto Sans SC&#x27;, &#x27;Noto Serif&#x27;, &#x27;Noto Serif SC&#x27;, &#x27;PingFang SC&#x27;, &#x27;Microsoft YaHei&#x27;, Sans-serif, Serif&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="深色模式"><a href="#深色模式" class="headerlink" title="深色模式"></a>深色模式</h3><p>依赖<code>nickdeny/darkmode.js</code></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#主题目录下的_config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># darkmode 深色模式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">darkmode:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">start_at:</span> <span class="number">24</span><span class="string">:00</span> <span class="comment"># time to start dark theme 自动切换深色模式的开始时间</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">end_at:</span> <span class="number">06</span><span class="string">:00</span> <span class="comment"># time to end dark theme 自动切换深色模式的结束时间</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">check_system_scheme:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># check if system indicates light or dark color themes 检查系统是否指定模式</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">save_on_toggle:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># save current mode in local storage 在本地保存现有模式</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="搜索功能"><a href="#搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="搜索功能"></a>搜索功能</h3><p>依赖<code>hexo-generator-search</code>插件</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#根目录下的_config.yml文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Search function</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">template:</span> <span class="string">./search.xml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在根目录下的<code>node_modules</code>文件夹中找到<code>hexo-generator-search</code>文件夹，再进入其中的<code>templates</code>文件夹，将构建搜索内容xml的模板文件<code>search.xml</code>复制到博客根目录下</p><p>搜索功能打开。</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#主题目录下的`_config.yml`</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="评论功能"><a href="#评论功能" class="headerlink" title="评论功能"></a>评论功能</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#主题目录下的_config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">comment:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post_enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 在文章页面增加评论模块</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">about_enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 在关于页增加评论模块</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>前置依照<a href="https://giscus.app/">giscus</a>官方文档弄</p><h3 id="语言配置"><a href="#语言配置" class="headerlink" title="语言配置"></a>语言配置</h3><p>仅有en 和zh-CN</p><p>针对不同的文章或页面，可以单独在文章&#x2F;页面的Front-matter信息中进行语言设置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lang: en</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果需要自定义界面上的各项显示值，可以在主题目录下的<code>languages</code>文件夹中找到对应的语言文件，然后修改对应的参数。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
